{"title":"Radar Roundup: Crust Mega Raffle Fundraiser for Leo, Chris King Guest House 2023, All Bodies on Bikes + Bobby, Mid South x Topo Designs + Event Weekend Video, and WTB x Shawn Neer","link":"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-crust-mega-raffle-fundraiser-for-leo-chris-king-guest-house-2023-all-bodies-on-bikes-bobby-mid-south-x-topo-designs-event-weekend-video-and-wtb-x-shawn-neer/","date":1680791208000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?w=1280&amp;quality=75 1280w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<p>Our Radar Roundup compiles products and videos from the ‘net in an easy-to-digest format. Read on below for today’s findings…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2165\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?w=2165&amp;quality=75 2165w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=1024,639&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=2000,1247&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=768,479&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=1800,1122&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=1335,832&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=700,436&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=1536,958&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339651365_1583849958779244_3364310280968410234_n.jpg?resize=2048,1277&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/leo-rodgers-needs-your-help\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bikes x Rivendell x Paul x Topo x Ron’s Bikes Raffle</a></h3>\n<p>Our friend, Leo was involved in a terrible bicycle accident a week before Christmas 2022.<br />\nHe was sadly left with limited mobility from the neck down, he is currently going through PT and some serious life style changes on his road to recovery. Crust Bikes have organized a Mega Raffle to help raise funds for Leo during this time. Leo has always been the life of the party and the positive energy in our community.</p>\n<p>Let’s show Leo he is not alone. He needs our love and support.</p>\n<p>A total of 5 prizes will be given away. To enter please donate $21 to <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/leo-rodgers-needs-your-help\" target=\"_blank\">Leo’s Gofundme</a>. </p>\n<p>Screenshot your receipt with the subject LEO MEGA RAFFLE. Email to <a href=\"mailto:winbig@crustbikes.com\" target=\"_blank\">winbig@crustbikes.com</a></p>\n<p>The winner will be announced on April 26 on Crust Bikes Instagram.</p>\n<p>We love you, Leo.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?resize=1024,819&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?resize=768,614&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?resize=1335,1068&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?resize=700,560&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Guest-House-2023-Flyer-HR-1.jpg?resize=1536,1229&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://chrisking.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King Guest House 2023</a></h3>\n<p>Tuesday, April 18th brings about the Chris King Guest House again! <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/chris-king-guest-house-2022/\" target=\"_blank\">Remember last year’s coverage</a>? Didn’t it look fun? Lots of bikes, products, and food in lovely Santa Cruz, Califonia? Yeah? Well go this year! It’ll be at Santa Cruz Bicycles and have all that above and more. </p>\n<p>Oh and ride Mailboxes for us! xo</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/0HCCZlwKzjjLLZv5DxP6D4aW-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/585aVTDsaXLlQgBKshzyw4?si=Rb1ZPrSZTaCUpBVtQ38ynQ&amp;context=spotify%3Ashow%3A5Hy9DyPF6b4pNvzk6jjd1X&amp;nd=1&amp;utm_medium=sharing&amp;_branch_referrer=H4sIAAAAAAAAAw3ESQ6CMAAAwNfgUZTFqIkxRQTZFAj7xVAKoSwCFrHwep3DlOPYkyPLkr4bcTGvG%2FyqWVP%2FvmnBacYMzwXMGoxONgApVB26XOwND1PgSqTSkofb0QOfx4JTDpxWOjUJkhsUtqbqAZTjPc1wsjOd1ROfZGOSE4%2FhlLvtx9cQRbMFMt1fJGOiZMgrJHqKELh%2BY%2BW8z3ASaMX%2FBUVT1tYgCsHApx%2FtB%2Fw%2FONyvAAAA&amp;fbclid=PAAabGQxzCP03baARBsjIZORox93eY4Qhq2IhQksVZHb41LGTAdei8xciZ6LQ&amp;_i=DKvDZT%2FNPUYEWdXyMAcJUzBKvxsqejd5TF4VRUlMe3U%2BAm5%2BfxdvcmkAXWAq3auI&amp;_branch_match_id=1172340683259791440\" target=\"_blank\">All Bodies on Bikes + Bobby Wintle</a></h3>\n<p>This week Marley from All Bodies on Bikes recaps her experience at Mid South Gravel! Join ABOB for on-the-ground conversations showcasing how joyful, fun, and inclusive the event was. She also got a chance to sit down with Bobby Wintle and share more about the event form his perspective.</p>\n<p>Bobby Wintle is the co-owner of District Bicycles and The Mid South both located in Stillwater, OK. For the last 11 years he has been building real community through the shop and The Mid South has now grown into one of the top 5 biggest gravel/dirt road events in the world. Bobby loves cooking Brussel sprouts on Cast Iron and could stare at a sunset and cry for hours. </p>\n<p>Give it a listen on <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/585aVTDsaXLlQgBKshzyw4?si=Rb1ZPrSZTaCUpBVtQ38ynQ&amp;context=spotify%3Ashow%3A5Hy9DyPF6b4pNvzk6jjd1X&amp;nd=1&amp;utm_medium=sharing&amp;_branch_referrer=H4sIAAAAAAAAAw3ESQ6CMAAAwNfgUZTFqIkxRQTZFAj7xVAKoSwCFrHwep3DlOPYkyPLkr4bcTGvG%2FyqWVP%2FvmnBacYMzwXMGoxONgApVB26XOwND1PgSqTSkofb0QOfx4JTDpxWOjUJkhsUtqbqAZTjPc1wsjOd1ROfZGOSE4%2FhlLvtx9cQRbMFMt1fJGOiZMgrJHqKELh%2BY%2BW8z3ASaMX%2FBUVT1tYgCsHApx%2FtB%2Fw%2FONyvAAAA&amp;fbclid=PAAabGQxzCP03baARBsjIZORox93eY4Qhq2IhQksVZHb41LGTAdei8xciZ6LQ&amp;_i=DKvDZT%2FNPUYEWdXyMAcJUzBKvxsqejd5TF4VRUlMe3U%2BAm5%2BfxdvcmkAXWAq3auI&amp;_branch_match_id=1172340683259791440\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a> or wherever you get your podcasts…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-5.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-5.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-5.jpg?resize=1024,1280&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-5.jpg?resize=768,960&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-5.jpg?resize=700,875&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-4.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-4.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-4.jpg?resize=1024,1280&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-4.jpg?resize=768,960&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/Topo-Dirts_preorder-4.jpg?resize=700,875&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.midsouthgravel.com/shop/p/topo-designs-x-the-mid-south-dirt-shirt-olive\" target=\"_blank\">Topo Designs x Mid South Dirt Shirt Pre-Order</a> $109</h3>\n<p><em>The pre-order window will be open until 11:59 p.m. CST April 7, 2023. Items will ship 2-3 weeks after order.<br />\nAvailability varies based on cut and size.</em></p>\n<p>Part of Topo’s Dirt Collection, this custom embroidered organic cotton shirt holds up to anything you throw at it. Mid South is selling a co-branded Dirt Shirt with the Mid South logos embroidered on it. With a straight fit, classic detailing and a single pocket, the Dirt Shirt will quickly become one of your go-to pieces. The garment dyed wash softens both the color and fabric, making it feel like an old favorite from its first wear.</p>\n<p>Roll on over to the <a href=\"https://www.midsouthgravel.com/shop/p/topo-designs-x-the-mid-south-dirt-shirt-olive\" target=\"_blank\">Mid South</a> to pre-order.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vM49pdyKu8E\" target=\"_blank\">The Mid South 2023 Event Weekend</a></h3>\n<p>The Mid South 2023 was a real blast and this recap video captures the vibes so well!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qVB3xsv0uF0\" target=\"_blank\">WTB x Shawn Neer</a></h3>\n<p>Shawn Neer has joined the WTB family and boy that guy can ride, man!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?w=1280&amp;quality=75 1280w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/339478676_939977813649207_1078572722262116781_n.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<p><i>Illustration via <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CqqPAVWpFEf/?igshid=ZGVhYjU3OTE%3D\" target=\"_blank\">@Cosmicearthworm<br />\n</a></i></p>\n<p>Artist Shelby Ling knows how to capture springtime vibes!</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, simply tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-crust-mega-raffle-fundraiser-for-leo-chris-king-guest-house-2023-all-bodies-on-bikes-bobby-mid-south-x-topo-designs-event-weekend-video-and-wtb-x-shawn-neer/\">Radar Roundup: Crust Mega Raffle Fundraiser for Leo, Chris King Guest House 2023, All Bodies on Bikes + Bobby, Mid South x Topo Designs + Event Weekend Video, and WTB x Shawn Neer</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"1ad756c9230565ef52fb1740fb2df66c1a5342d6f9a927e6704d5edb4e123013","category":"Cycling"}